252
00:10:58,091 --> 00:10:59,259
Did we hit something?

253
00:10:59,425 --> 00:11:00,126
Hey, Boss!

254
00:11:00,126 --> 00:11:01,127
You just hit something!

255
00:11:01,127 --> 00:11:02,529
It just went flying!

256
