or tie me up.

265
00:11:20,680 --> 00:11:21,881
But how strange.

266
00:11:22,015 --> 00:11:24,250
I find I'm beginning to love hearing
his harsh words.

267
00:11:24,250 --> 00:11:25,685
Please just shut the hell up!

268
00:11:25,685 --> 00:11:26,386
Pretty please!

269
00:11:26,386 --> 00:11:27,086
Now what is this?

270
00:11:27,086 --> 00:11:28,121
"Pretty please?"

271
00:11:28,121 --> 00:11:29,689
