You're totally clueless!

275
00:11:35,662 --> 00:11:38,298
Like a teenage girl trying on
make up for the first time!

276
00:11:44,137 --> 00:11:45,972
You have hurt Elizabeth!

277
00:11:46,573 --> 00:11:48,308
And I will not forgive you.

278
00:11:49,075 --> 00:11:50,276
No!

279
00:11:52,312 --> 00:11:54,013
So you've come for me
at last, assassin!

280
00:11:57,383 --> 00:11:58,384
We're scraping the wall!

281
00:11:58,384 --> 00:11:59,786
Sparks!
On both sides of the car!

282
00:11:59,786 --> 00:12:00,853
Do you see...

283
00:12:00,987 --> 00:12:02,855
my special driving technique?

284
00:12:03,122 --> 00:12:04,190
That's no technique!

285
00:12:04,190 --> 00:12:06,225
All I'm hearing is squeak and shriek!

286
00:12:06,392 --> 00:12:08,061
Come on, Kondo, and shut up.

287
00:12:08,061 --> 00:12:08,795
Hey!

288
00:12:08,795 --> 00:12:10,530
Look!
Look out ahead!

289
00:12:10,663 --> 00:12:12,932
Don't worry, I'm Schumacher, you know!

290
00:12:18,338 --> 00:12:19,272
That was close.

291
00:12:19,272 --> 00:12:20,707
The assassin totally wrecked the car!

292
00:12:20,707 --> 00:12:21,808
Assassin?
Where is he?

293
00:12:21,808 --> 00:12:22,609
Where's the assasin?

294
00:12:22,609 --> 00:12:24,644
You totally crashed the car yourself!

295
00:12:24,911 --> 00:12:27,080
You know, a kind person
takes all the blame,

296
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:28,581
and ends up hurting himself.

297
00:12:29,549 --> 00:12:30,984
What are you going to do now?

298
00:12:30,984 --> 00:12:33,052
Because now we don't have
any transportation.

299
00:12:33,052 --> 00:12:33,987
Huh?

300
00:12:34,253 --> 00:12:36,656
Hee, hoo, hee, hoo, hee, hoo, hee, hoo,
hee, hoo, hee, hoo, hee, hoo, hee, hoo,

301
