This is an emergency.

304
00:12:43,029 --> 00:12:44,631
We should commandeer that bicycle.

305
00:12:45,898 --> 00:12:46,899
Wait, where are you going!

306
00:12:47,033 --> 00:12:49,402
I have a bad feeling about that bicycle.

307
00:12:49,936 --> 00:12:51,771
It's punishment!
It's punishment, right?

308
00:12:51,771 --> 00:12:53,439
Because I want to be punished!

309
00:12:53,439 --> 00:12:55,208
I love Punishment!

310
00:12:55,208 --> 00:12:57,410
Cut it out, already, crazy lady!

311
00:13:14,394 --> 00:13:16,029
What a mess this whole situation is!

312
00:13:16,029 --> 00:13:18,831
For the sake of those poor innocent
people who gave us this bike,

313
00:13:18,831 --> 00:13:21,334
we have to get to the
castle alive, no matter what!

314
00:13:21,868 --> 00:13:25,838
Hee hoo, hee hoo, hee hoo,
hee hoo I wonder why?

315
00:13:26,439 --> 00:13:29,242
All of a sudden, I can see nothing
but darkness ahead.

316
00:13:29,642 --> 00:13:31,144
Is this a reflection of my soul?

317
00:13:31,144 --> 00:13:32,478
When did it become so dark?

318
00:13:32,478 --> 00:13:33,446
Huh?
No!

319
00:13:33,446 --> 00:13:35,381
