Right there!

324
00:13:40,420 --> 00:13:42,789
Aaaaah!

325
00:13:44,924 --> 00:13:46,426
It disappeared!
It disappeared!

326
00:13:46,426 --> 00:13:47,894
My darkness disappeared!

327
00:13:50,763 --> 00:13:51,597
I'm done.

328
00:13:51,597 --> 00:13:53,066
I am so done.

329
