I should've just gone home.

330
00:13:59,539 --> 00:14:00,673
Hm?..

331
00:14:01,040 --> 00:14:02,642
What the heck is that over there?

332
00:14:02,642 --> 00:14:05,278
It's just a sad bunch of
edgy attention seekers

333
00:14:05,278 --> 00:14:07,914
who think they're on a
vacation riding a bike.

334
00:14:08,948 --> 00:14:11,117
At least they aren't causing
anyone any trouble.

335
00:14:11,417 --> 00:14:14,287
I really don't know what to do about
those losers living above my bar.

336
00:14:14,287 --> 00:14:17,223
They come up with so many
excuses to not pay their rent!

337
00:14:17,223 --> 00:14:20,293
But my patience is wearing thin
and is about to reach its limit!

338
00:14:20,460 --> 00:14:22,628
You're acting as if they
owe you the rent!

339
00:14:23,629 --> 00:14:24,797
Hey, Kondo.

340
00:14:25,064 --> 00:14:26,232
Do you see them?

341
00:14:26,365 --> 00:14:28,167
They are assassins.

342
00:14:28,801 --> 00:14:30,369
