344
00:14:33,139 --> 00:14:34,741
Look at their dark auras.

345
00:14:34,974 --> 00:14:36,109
There's no doubt.

346
00:14:36,309 --> 00:14:37,877
Yes, I can see it as well.

347
00:14:38,077 --> 00:14:38,811
What?

348
00:14:38,811 --> 00:14:40,046
Their postures.

349
00:14:40,046 --> 00:14:41,914
Only those who carry
the deepest sorrows

350
00:14:41,914 --> 00:14:43,649
within can strike that kind of pose.

351
00:14:43,649 --> 00:14:45,118
What the hell are you talking about?

352
00:14:45,118 --> 00:14:47,320
I can't see it, so come on, guys!

353
00:14:47,487 --> 00:14:49,655
Let's kill them before they kill us!

354
00:15:01,100 --> 00:15:02,068
This is..

355
00:15:02,235 --> 00:15:03,603
a pedestrian road!

356
00:15:04,337 --> 00:15:05,438
Yes, Ma'am.

357
00:15:09,709 --> 00:15:11,744
Well, things like this happen.

358
00:15:12,078 --> 00:15:13,079
No way!

359
00:15:13,212 --> 00:15:15,181
I was just so scared of them!

360
00:15:15,281 --> 00:15:17,717
I thought I might piss my pants
at this old age you know.

361
00:15:17,717 --> 00:15:20,586
Yeah, well, your eyes are certainly
pissing alright.

362
00:15:25,091 --> 00:15:27,960
There, there, fluffy things!

363
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:30,463
How many of them would you like,
Mr. Amanto?

364
00:15:31,464 --> 00:15:32,765
G, all of them.

365
00:15:32,765 --> 00:15:34,634
Get every last one of them.

366
00:15:34,634 --> 00:15:38,204
You manage to act like a jobless loser
who never leaves his mommy's nest.

367
00:15:38,204 --> 00:15:39,539
Well done, Prince!

368
00:15:40,406 --> 00:15:41,808
They're so fluffy!

369
00:15:42,041 --> 00:15:43,209
So cute!

370
00:15:47,046 --> 00:15:48,848
I finally found you, assassin.

371
00:15:48,848 --> 00:15:49,782
Seriously.

372
00:15:49,782 --> 00:15:51,317
I can't keep up with this crap.

373
00:15:51,317 --> 00:15:52,919
W‐What are you doing?!

374
00:15:52,919 --> 00:15:54,687
Don't you know, I'm Prince Hata!

375
00:15:54,987 --> 00:15:56,789
‐Prince Kaka?
‐Not Kaka!

376
00:15:56,789 --> 00:15:58,524
It's Prince Hata.
Hata!

377
00:15:58,524 --> 00:16:00,159
G! Do something!

378
00:16:00,159 --> 00:16:01,093
Sir!

379
00:16:02,695 --> 00:16:03,796
Umm so...

380
00:16:04,163 --> 00:16:05,198
I'm so sorry!

381
00:16:05,198 --> 00:16:07,433
You can take him,
but please spare me!

382
00:16:08,134 --> 00:16:09,101
All right.

383
00:16:09,235 --> 00:16:11,330
But in exchange, can I take your car?

384
00:16:11,337 --> 00:16:12,872
Of course, if you let me live!

385
00:16:13,105 --> 00:16:14,006
Hey!

386
00:16:14,140 --> 00:16:15,308
Wha?

387
00:16:15,775 --> 00:16:16,909
We don't have time.
Hurry up!

388
00:16:16,909 --> 00:16:17,710
All right!

389
00:16:18,311 --> 00:16:20,079
Why did you let those two go?

390
00:16:20,079 --> 00:16:21,314
I thought they're assasins.

391
00:16:21,314 --> 00:16:23,282
Well, they were just small fries.

392
00:16:26,085 --> 00:16:27,820
Hi, fancy seeing you here!

393
00:16:27,820 --> 00:16:28,955
You're shopping here, too?

394
00:16:28,955 --> 00:16:30,990
What a surprise to see you
in this kind of place.

395
00:16:30,990 --> 00:16:34,160
As I thought, you and I are
destined to be together, Otae!

396
00:16:34,327 --> 00:16:35,328
Oh,my goodness.

397
00:16:35,328 --> 00:16:37,663
Looks like a gorilla has
escaped from the zoo.

398
00:16:37,663 --> 00:16:41,167
