and have it shot dead ASAP.

399
00:16:41,367 --> 00:16:43,269
Let's see, their catch phrase is.

400
00:16:43,402 --> 00:16:46,606
"Call us and they're dead
as a Dodo, we promise!"

401
00:16:46,706 --> 00:16:47,740
Otae, please!

402
00:16:47,740 --> 00:16:49,609
Are you kidding me right now?

403
00:16:49,609 --> 00:16:50,610
It's me, Kondo!

404
00:16:50,610 --> 00:16:52,111
It's your Kondo!

405
00:16:52,278 --> 00:16:53,279
Such a bad gorilla!

406
00:16:53,279 --> 00:16:54,747
He's threatening me!

407
00:16:55,214 --> 00:16:57,283
You should know your place, gorilla!

408
00:16:57,283 --> 00:16:59,252
Now I'm going to show you!

409
00:17:06,526 --> 00:17:08,728
Today's unluckiest horoscope is.

410
00:17:08,728 --> 00:17:10,162
The sign of a Virgo.

411
00:17:10,563 --> 00:17:11,998
You're dying today!

412
00:17:12,465 --> 00:17:14,100
I die today...

413
00:17:14,333 --> 00:17:15,701
Stop it Sis!

414
00:17:15,701 --> 00:17:17,370
He's not a gorilla!
He's Kondo!

415
00:17:17,370 --> 00:17:18,838
Not a gorilla at all!

416
00:17:19,839 --> 00:17:22,375
Oh my, if it isn't Kondo
all of a sudden.

417
00:17:22,475 --> 00:17:24,777
It was always him, Sis.
It was Kondo from the start!

418
00:17:38,190 --> 00:17:41,661
I'll shoot you if you don't start driving
by the time I finish counting to ten.

419
00:17:41,861 --> 00:17:42,695
Ten.

420
00:17:42,695 --> 00:17:44,030
You didn't even count!

421
00:17:44,030 --> 00:17:45,464
You just missed me!

422
00:17:45,831 --> 00:17:46,532
So close!

423
00:17:46,532 --> 00:17:48,200
Otae, what did you just say?

424
00:17:48,334 --> 00:17:49,502
Do you really wish I was dead?

425
00:17:49,502 --> 00:17:50,636
No way!

426
00:17:56,876 --> 00:17:57,710
I've got it!

427
00:17:57,710 --> 00:17:59,312
This breadstick is
from Olive Garden!

428
00:17:59,312 --> 00:18:01,847
This barbeque sauce is
from Outback Steakhouse.

429
00:18:01,847 --> 00:18:04,116
And this dip is from Red Lobster.

430
00:18:04,116 --> 00:18:05,785
I see they've changed the recipe.

431
00:18:06,385 --> 00:18:09,121
You're so amazing, Kagura!

432
00:18:09,121 --> 00:18:11,090
Call me "Ultimate Tongue."

433
00:18:14,660 --> 00:18:15,828
Running out of gas?

434
00:18:15,962 --> 00:18:17,530
I bet you're an assassin, too!

435
00:18:17,530 --> 00:18:18,230
Yeah.

436
00:18:18,230 --> 00:18:19,865
We'll be replaced by this gorilla before

437
00:18:19,865 --> 00:18:20,833
