‐B‐Boss!

438
00:18:20,833 --> 00:18:22,301
Please calm down, I beg you.

439
00:18:22,301 --> 00:18:25,404
It's my last wish!
My last wish!

440
00:18:25,538 --> 00:18:26,339
Really?

441
00:18:26,472 --> 00:18:28,774
