do you have, then?

442
00:18:28,908 --> 00:18:30,276
It's my first wish!
My first wish!

443
00:18:30,276 --> 00:18:31,544
Hey!

444
00:18:32,611 --> 00:18:33,512
That's it!

445
00:18:33,512 --> 00:18:34,647
Whoa!

446
00:18:39,485 --> 00:18:42,521
Let's go, amazing gorilla power!

447
00:18:42,989 --> 00:18:43,689
Oooh.
Oh, no.

448
00:18:43,689 --> 00:18:45,891
