that he is a gorilla.

449
00:18:46,025 --> 00:18:49,528
Well, I guess it's better for him to
realize who he really is.

450
00:18:49,528 --> 00:18:52,331
Hey! How can you guys
just relax back there?

451
00:18:57,036 --> 00:18:59,005
You can't run from your sins,
you know.

452
00:18:59,739 --> 00:19:01,073
Face your death!

453
00:19:01,774 --> 00:19:03,409
Oh, my!
What a giant peppermint.

454
00:19:03,409 --> 00:19:06,512
With a size this large, it can save
the entire city from bad breath.

455
00:19:06,679 --> 00:19:08,147
Whoa!
It's a bomb!

456
00:19:08,147 --> 00:19:09,515
Throw it!
Hurry!

457
00:19:09,849 --> 00:19:11,150
Where are my glasses?

458
00:19:11,317 --> 00:19:12,518
I need my glasses.

459
00:19:12,518 --> 00:19:14,920
‐I need my glasses to.
‐Just throw it already!

460
00:19:15,054 --> 00:19:16,022
Here we go!

461
00:19:16,022 --> 00:19:17,590
Get down everyone!

462
00:19:19,625 --> 00:19:20,693
Huh?

463
00:19:20,693 --> 00:19:21,861
Oh! it's you.

464
00:19:24,797 --> 00:19:26,298
‐OH!
‐OH!

465
00:19:26,632 --> 00:19:28,034
Holy.

466
00:19:30,536 --> 00:19:31,504
Eh?

467
00:19:31,671 --> 00:19:32,438
What?

468
00:19:32,438 --> 00:19:33,706
Was that my booger?

469
00:19:33,739 --> 00:19:35,508
Did my booger just do that?

470
00:19:41,714 --> 00:19:43,015
It's time, Kondo.

471
00:20:02,101 --> 00:20:05,404
Commissioner of National Police,
Katakuriko Matsudaira.

472
00:20:05,905 --> 00:20:08,507
And Shinsengumi chief, Isao Kondo.

473
00:20:09,542 --> 00:20:11,310
Here, at your service, sirs!

474
00:20:13,446 --> 00:20:14,980
Yes.
Very good.

475
00:20:15,314 --> 00:20:17,983
Today, I've called you here
because of the incident

476
00:20:17,983 --> 00:20:20,953
