regarding the underground arena,

477
00:20:20,953 --> 00:20:22,588
the Purgatory.

478
00:20:24,423 --> 00:20:26,559
Did something happen to you two?

479
00:20:26,559 --> 00:20:27,493
Nothing.

480
00:20:27,626 --> 00:20:29,929
Just some trouble baking
some pecan pies.

481
00:20:31,797 --> 00:20:34,400
