did an awesome job.

487
00:20:49,148 --> 00:20:49,915
Yes...

488
00:20:49,915 --> 00:20:51,750
you and your men were
quite impressive.

489
00:20:51,750 --> 00:20:53,018
Thanks to you,

490
00:20:53,152 --> 00:20:55,121
we have maintained
a serene balance

491
00:20:55,121 --> 00:20:57,356
between the Amanto
and the Earthlings.

492
00:20:57,523 --> 00:20:58,891
I commend you both.

493
00:21:00,192 --> 00:21:03,262
