502
00:21:34,059 --> 00:21:35,094
Well yeah.

503
00:21:35,094 --> 00:21:38,330
I think we had been misunderstanding
their intentions all along.

504
00:21:38,531 --> 00:21:40,166
That was a really fierce fight.

505
00:21:40,566 --> 00:21:43,669
One of the top five closest
calls of my entire life.

506
00:21:43,802 --> 00:21:44,737
Hey, Pops,

507
00:21:44,737 --> 00:21:47,840
